모델| 크기  
(MB)| 파라미터  
(M)| 속도 (CPU)  
(ms/im)  
---|---|---|---  
[Meta SAM-b](/ko/models/sam)| 375| 93.7| 41703  
Meta SAM 2-b| 162| 80.8| 28867  
Meta SAM 2-t| 78.1| 38.9| 23430  
[MobileSAM](/ko/models/mobile-sam)| 40.7| 10.1| 23802  
[FastSAM-s](/ko/models/fast-sam) with YOLOv8 [backbone](https://www.ultralytics.com/glossary/backbone)| 23.9| 11.8| 58.0  
